title: Static Analysis

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to configured Wi-Fi networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA.description: Access extra location provider commands. Malicious applications could use this to interfere with the operation of the GPS or other location sources.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

com.vznavigator.Generic.permission.C2D_M.description: Allows the application to receive push notifications.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.CALL_PHONE.description: Allows the application to call phone numbers without your intervention. Malicious applications may cause unexpected calls on your phone bill. Note that this does not allow the application to call emergency numbers.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH.description: Allows an application to view configuration of the local Bluetooth phone and to make and accept connections with paired devices.

android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.

android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD.description: Allows an application to disable the key lock and any associated password security. A legitimate example of this is the phone disabling the key lock when receiving an incoming phone call, then re-enabling the key lock when the call is finished.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.REQUEST_IGNORE_BATTER.description: Permission an application must hold in order to use

android.permission.KILL_BACKGROUND_PROCE.description: Allows an application to kill background processes of other applications, even if memory is not low.

manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

manifest_analysis.title:
Application Data can be Backed up
[android:allowBackup=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: This flag allows anyone to backup your application data via adb. It allows users who have enabled USB debugging to copy application data off of the device.
manifest_analysis.name: Application Data can be Backed up [android:allowBackup=true]

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.navbuilder.app.nexgen.MainActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.

"IDS_CONDITION_TEXT_LINE2" : "to our Terms & Conditions and Privacy Policy"
"IDS_CONNECTION_ERROR" : "Please check your connection and try again"
"IDS_CONNECTION_NOT_AVAILABLE_PLEASE" : "Connection not available. Please try again later."

"IDS_CONTACT_CARRIER_ROADSIDE" : "Connect to a Verizon Wireless Roadside Assistance representative for service including Towing, Battery Jump, Flat Tire Service, Fuel delivery and more. One-time service option ($69.95) or membership for $3/mo (48hr waiting period). To enroll in Roadside Assistance program, dial *611 from your phone to speak to a representative."
"IDS_CORRUPT_DATA_DETECTED_INVALID" : "Corrupt data detected. Invalid records have been removed."
"IDS_COULD_NOT_GET_A_ROUTE_BETWEEN" : "A valid route can't be found. Try entering a different start or end point."
"IDS_COULD_NOT_PROCESS_YOUR_GPS" : "Could not process your GPS request. Please try again."
"IDS_COULD_NOT_PROCESS_YOUR_REQUEST" : "Could not process your request. Please try again."
"IDS_COULD_NOT_PROCESS_YOUR_REQUEST_HTTP_ERROR" : "Could not process your request due to an HTTP error."

"IDS_DUE_TO_INSUFFICIENT" : "Due to insufficient permissions, VZ Navigator will exit now.

To use the application, please check your Location and Phone permission settings."
"IDS_ERROR_AIRPLANE_MODE" : "VZ Navigator is having trouble finding your current position. Please make sure the phone is not in airplane mode and your battery is charged."
"IDS_ERROR_CONNECTING_TO_FACEBOOK" : "VZ Navigator is having trouble communicating with Facebook. Please try again later."
"IDS_ERROR_DESTINATION_NOT_NEAR_A_ROAD" : "Your chosen destination is not on or near a road and VZ Navigator cannot provide directions to that location. Please change the destination and try again."
"IDS_ERROR_FINDING_YOUR_LOCATION" : "VZ Navigator is having trouble finding your current position. Please try again."
"IDS_ERROR_INVALID_ACTIVATION_CODE" : "The activation code you are trying to enter is not valid. Please try entering your activation code again."
"IDS_ERROR_INVALID_DESTINATION" : "VZ Navigator is having trouble routing you to your destination. Please try a different start or end point."
"IDS_ERROR_LOCATION_SETTING" : "VZ Navigator is unable to find your location. Please ensure your GPS and location settings are enabled."
"IDS_ERROR_MDN_INACTIVE" : "It appears that this phone number is not an active VZ Navigator subscriber."
"IDS_ERROR_NAV_VOICE_CALL" : "In order to find your current location or continue your trip, you must end your current voice call. Please end the call and try again."
"IDS_ERROR_NO_MAP_DATA" : "VZ Navigator is unable to find map data for the requested location. Please change the location and try again."
"IDS_ERROR_NO_RESULTS" : "No results were found for your search. Please change your search terms and try again."
"IDS_ERROR_PERMISSION_SETTINGS" : "Your application permission settings will not allow use of VZ Navigator."
"IDS_ERROR_PRIVACY_SETTING" : "Permission to get your GPS location was denied by your privacy settings. Acceptance of privacy permissions is required."
"IDS_ERROR_RECHARGE_BATTERY" : "VZ Navigator is having trouble finding your current position. Please recharge your battery and try again."
"IDS_ERROR_RESET_BATTERY" : "Your GPS location request could not be processed. You may need to restart your device by removing and replacing your battery."
"IDS_ERROR_SENDING_REQUEST" : "There was a problem with your request. Please restart VZ Navigator and try again."
"IDS_ERROR_SERVER_COMMUNICATION" : "VZ Navigator is having trouble communicating with its servers. Please try again."
"IDS_ERROR_START_NOT_NEAR_A_ROAD" : "The beginning of your route is too far away from a road. Please proceed to the nearest road and try again."
"IDS_ERROR_UNSUPPORTED_REGION" : "This feature is not available for this location."
"IDS_ERROR_UPDATING_ROUTE" : "There was a problem while getting your route. Please check your route options and try again."

"IDS_ERROR_WEAK_SIGNAL" : "VZ Navigator is having trouble finding your current position. This may be due to poor signal or low battery life. Please ensure you are in good network coverage and try again."
"IDS_EULA_CONTENT" : "This content is pulled from the server. If you do not see something here then check the server eula message settings."
"IDS_EXIT_APP_CONFIRM" : "Do you want to exit the app?"

"IDS_EXPLORE_DESCRIPTION" : "From the Explore panel, select from popular brands or categories to do a search nearby, or even add your own quick-searches to personalize your experience. Drag and drop to re-arrange. Your top 6 will appear on your home screen for easy access."
"IDS_FAILED_TO_READ_FROM_A_NETWORK" : "Failed to read from a network socket"
"IDS_FAILED_TO_WRITE_TO_A_NETWORK" : "Failed to write to a network socket"

"IDS_FAVORITES_DESCRIPTION" : "Customize your Favorites by adding and pinning the places that are important to you such as your home, work, school, or gym. Press and hold to pin, edit or delete. Your three pinned favorites will appear on your home screen and will be monitored for real-time traffic conditions and ETA. Delete individual Favorites and Recents by swiping them left."
"IDS_FINDING_YOUR_LOCATION_FOR_BEST" : "Finding your location. For best performance you must be in an area with a clear view of the sky."

"IDS_FIND_THE_CHEAPEST_GAS" : "Find the cheapest
 gas prices near you"

"IDS_GAS_DESCRIPTION" : "VZ Navigator makes it especially easy to find nearby gas stations, whether you care about price, brand or convenience. Simply tap on the gas icon in the Explore panel or use the search box to find gas stations near you. The search results will show price information and highlight the least expensive option that is near you. If you want more information about the station, such as if they offer specialty fuel like diesel, just tap to get the details."
"IDS_GENERAL_ERROR_ONE_OR_MORE" : "General error. One or more of the parameters is null"
"IDS_GENERAL_ERROR_THAT_COULD_BE" : "General error that could be reported through an HTTP response code or a service-specific error"
"IDS_HIGHWAY_SIGN_CONTENT" : "Realistic highway signs allow you to stay informed about upcoming junctions, lane changes and exits."
"IDS_LATITUDE_OR_LONGITUDE_IS_OUT_OF_RANGE" : "Latitude or longitude is out of range"

"IDS_LOCALDEALS_DESCRIPTION" : "Included with a monthly subscription, Local Deals, powered by Entertainment®, gives you quick access to hundreds of dollars of instant discounts locally and across the country. First, tap the deal you want. Next, tap redeem when you are ready. Finally, show your screen to your server or cashier to save."
"IDS_LOCALE_CHANGED_DETECTION" : "Language change detected, please restart your app."
"IDS_MESSAGE_APPNAME_AUTH_ERROR" : "VZ Navigator has encountered a problem verifying authorization. Please exit and resubscribe to VZ Navigator."
"IDS_MESSAGE_APPNAME_CHECK_ELIGIBILITY_FAILED" : "Unable to confirm your eligibility. Please click 'Call' VZ Navigator Customer Care, or click 'Exit' and try again later."
"IDS_MESSAGE_APPNAME_INELIGIBLE_USER" : "Your plan does not support this application. Please 'Call' VZ Navigator Customer Care to update your plan."
"IDS_MESSAGE_APPNAME_PURCHASE_ERROR" : "VZ Navigator has encountered a problem purchasing license. Please exit and try again."
"IDS_MESSAGE_BIND_LICENSE_FAILED" : "Unable to process your request at this time. Press 'OK' to exit and try again."

"IDS_MOVIES_DESCRIPTION" : "VZ Navigator user location and the current time to make finding movies, theaters and showtimes a fast, seamless experience. Select a movie to see its details along with nearby theaters and showtimes, or select a theater to see its location and its available movies and showtimes. Also, search for movies and theaters directly from the search box."

"IDS_NAVIGATION_DESCRIPTION_1" : "Our next-generation navigation experience does the work of finding your optimal route for you. Select Go to automatically navigate via the fastest route. Want to preview your route or see available alternate routes? Select View Routes and VZ Navigator will give you up to three routes to compare. Tap the route you want, and tap Go to start navigation."
"IDS_NAVIGATION_DESCRIPTION_2" : "Stick with the quickest option as the default, or choose an alternate with just a single tap. Tap Go to start navigation."

"IDS_NAV_NOTIFICATION_CONTENT" : "Do you still need navigation? You haven't moved for 5 minutes. To help conserve battery life we will end your navigation session if you continue to stay still for the next 5 minutes."
"IDS_NO_RESPONSE_WAS_RECEIVED_FROM" : "No response was received from the server within the allotted time"
"IDS_PEDESTRIAN_ROUTE_IS_TOO_LONG" : "This route is too long for this mode of transportation."

"IDS_PERSONALIZE_WITH_PLACES" : "Personalize with places
 that matter to you"

"IDS_PLEASE_ENABLE_THESE_OPTIONS" : "Please enable these options in your settings to ensure VZ Navigator work properly: 
 - Background data 
 - Unrestricted data usage (only applies if Data Saver is on)"
"IDS_PLEASE_ENSURE_THAT_THE_PHONE_YOU" : "Please ensure that the phone you are trying to locate is turned ON and within GPS coverage area."
"IDS_PLEASE_TAKE_A_MOMENT" : "Please take a moment to rate us. Have a suggestion, give us your feedback."
"IDS_PLEASE_TELL_US_ABOUT_MISSING_OR" : "Please tell us about missing or incorrect addresses or other product issues. For all billing issues please dial *611."

playstore_details.title: VZ Navigator
playstore_details.description:
Try the all new VZ Navigator FREE* for 30 Days and then pay only $4.99/month thereafter, or use it when you need it for just $0.99 for 24 hours of use.
VZ Navigator is a premium navigation application that provides the most complete, accurate, and easy-to-use navigation assistance available. Enhanced 3D maps, intuitive local search and natural turn-by-turn voice guidance get you to your destination quickly and efficiently.  Advanced features such as Doppler weather radar, gas prices, and movie showtimes give you valuable information to help save time and money. 

Simple and Adaptive Maps
With a focus on optimizing the user experience, the map has been totally redesigned.  Every feature, from the advanced gestures and unified color scheme to the high-fidelity landmarks and transparent 3D buildings has been expressly composed to balance simplicity and capability. Customizable map layers include real-time traffic, satellite view, Doppler weather radar, and favorites.

Personalized Local Searches
Search has been enhanced and is now better than ever. With TripAdvisor ratings and reviews integrated into points of interest, choosing local places to visit is a snap.  With our improved Gas Station search, effortlessly view and compare all nearby stations and prices on the map.  Our Movie search has also been overhauled to be easier to use, whether you’re just browsing or looking for specific movie or theater.  Additionally, you can add any store brand or place category to your Explore panel, allowing one-tap to find your favorite places no matter where you go.

Streamlined Navigation
Helping you confidently and safely maneuver around streets and highways on your journey is our primary goal.  Visual & Voice Lane Guidance and Realistic Highway Signs ensure you’re always in the right place at the right time while preparing for maneuvers.  Natural Voice Guidance provides references to real-world landmarks like stop signs and traffic lights to help you make turns with confidence.  Our navigation experience has been refreshed with real-time traffic integrated into your route, along with one-touch access to your upcoming maneuvers and route overview.  Plus, take advantage of our customizable Speed Limits & Alerts to stay safe – and possibly even avoid a ticket.
*Offer valid for new VZ Navigator subscribers. Limited time offer. Customer will automatically continue with the $4.99 monthly subscription after the 30 day trial period ends. Unsubscribe anytime using the “My Account” menu option in the app or by calling 1.800.922.0204 within 30 days of downloading the app to avoid being charged.
